General description
The general description will help you understand who exactly uses cookies to collect information from your device, for what purpose this information is used and how you can manage the use of cookies in relation to non-core activities.
If you opt out of the use of advertising cookies, you may still be able to see sweet.tv ads on other sites, however, such ads will not be personalized by us or our service providers for you, and we will continue to send you personalized offers when you use our website based on information from cookies that you have not opted out of.
Alternatively, in most browsers you can set your privacy settings to prevent your browser from accepting new cookies, to notify you when you receive new cookies, or to disable all cookies altogether. If your browser is configured not to accept cookies, you will not be shown interest-based ads, but your use of sweet.tv may be difficult or impossible. In addition, if you opt out of certain cookies using our cookie selection tool, your preferences will be saved by storing the cookie on your device. Therefore, it is important that your browser accepts cookies, otherwise your settings will not be applied. If you delete or clear cookies, or if you change the web browser you are using, you will need to set your cookie settings again.
For more information on our use of cookies, see the section on Cookies.
Mandatory cookies
These cookies are essential for our website to function. For example, we and our Service Providers may use these cookies to authenticate and identify visitors when they use our website so that we can provide services to them. They also help us enforce the Terms of Use, prevent fraudulent activities and keep our services secure.
Expiration date: most cookies are valid for one session (they are only active until you close your browser) or for a day. Some cookies remain active for a longer time, from 3 to 12 months.
Cookies for efficiency and functionality
These cookies help us improve and personalize your sweet.tv Internet experience. For example, they allow us to remember your settings and eliminate the need to re-enter previously provided information (for example, during user registration). We also use these cookies to collect information (in particular, popular pages, conversion rates, browsing habits, click-throughs and other information) about the use of the sweet.tv service by our visitors. This enables us to improve and personalize our website and service, as well as conduct market research. Removing these types of cookies may lead to a limitation of the functionality of our service.
Expiration date: most cookies are only active for 24 hours. Some cookies remain active for a longer time, from 3 to 12 months.
These cookies use information about your interactions with this and other websites, your reaction to ads and emails in order to display ads that are more relevant to you, as well as for analysis and optimization purposes. These types of ads are called “personalized ads” and are displayed outside the sweet.tv domain. Sweet.tv uses contractual and technical measures designed to prevent advertising partners from accessing information about the content you choose, the URLs of the sites you visit, or the movies and TV shows that you watched using our service.
We do not share information about the content you choose or the movies and TV shows you watch through our service.
Detailed information on "Consent to the processing of personal data by Cookies"
Welcome and thank you for using our services! To make your experience as informative and user-friendly as possible, we use Google Consent Mode along with other analytics and advertising services.
This consent agreement outlines how we collect, use, and share your data in compliance with data protection laws and your rights as a user.
Data Collection and Use:
Analytics: We collect anonymized data about your interactions and use of our website to understand user behavior, improve our services, and enhance user experience. This includes pages visited, session duration, and interaction with content.
Advertising: With your consent, we display personalized ads based on your browsing behavior and preferences. This helps us show you more relevant offers and products.
Consent Choices:
Accept All: By choosing 'Accept All', you consent to the use of cookies and similar technologies for both analytics and personalized advertising as described above.
Reject All: Selecting 'Reject All' will limit your experience to basic website features and non-personalized content. We will only use essential cookies necessary for the website's operation.
Customize: You have the option to customize your consent preferences, allowing you to choose specifically between analytics and advertising cookies.
Your Rights:
You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time, access the data collected about you, request correction or deletion of your data, and object to or restrict processing of your data. For any of these requests, please contact our Data Protection Officer at info@sweet.tv.
Changes to This Agreement:
We may update this consent agreement from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes and seek your consent where required by law.
By using our website, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this User Consent Agreement. If you have any questions or need further information, please do not hesitate to contact us.
